    "body": "Unit testing is a good idea for things that can be properly unit tested -- like the file format parsers (including sequences, rules, etc) and coordinate transforms (ideally also aspects of rendering, but that is going to be tricky without an offscreen rendering context).  It would also make sense to use NUnit to run the integration tests.\n"
